<template>
  <el-cascader-panel style="width: fit-content" :options="options"/>
</template>

<script setup>
import axios from "axios";
import {ref} from "vue";

let options = ref([]);

axios.get('http://localhost:8080/chapterselect').then((response) => {
  options.value = JSON.parse(response.data.data);
  // options.value = response.data;
